---
title: Speedy Prawn Rigatoni with courgette and parsley
description: Sometimes, you just want a big bowl of pasta and you don't want to wait. Luckily, you've got this speedy and super simple prawn rigatoni—perfect for just such an occasion.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF230112_R03_W10_IE_IEXQS0023-2_Main_high-caf668b6.jpg
